node.title: Jimmy Kimmel: The U.S. Is Finally Back at the Neighborhood BBQ
node.alt: “This is a traditional thing. It hasn’t been held since 2016 because — guess why?” Jimmy Kimmel said on Thursday.
node.description: “I think it’s nice that we’re friendly with our neighbors again,” Kimmel said of Biden’s meeting with leaders of Canada and Mexico.
node.content: ["Welcome to Best of Late Night, a rundown of the previous night\u2019s highlights that lets you sleep \u2014 and lets us get paid to watch comedy. Here are the 50 best movies on Netflix right now.", "President Biden met with Prime Minister Justin Trudeau of Canada and President Andr\u00e9s Manuel L\u00f3pez Obrador of Mexico at the White House on Thursday to talk trade and other issues \u2014 in the return of meetings after a five-year hiatus during the Trump administration.", "\u201cThis is a traditional thing. It hasn\u2019t been held since 2016 because \u2014 guess why?\u201d Jimmy Kimmel said on Thursday night.", "Jeff Goldblum sat down with Desus and Mero, and the actor ended up asking most of the questions.", "\u201cJagged\u201d documents Alanis Morissette\u2019s rise to fame with her hit 1995 album, \u201cJagged Little Pill.\u201d"]
